items.name: uuid
items.desc: The unique identifier for the call.

items.name: isOutgoing
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the call is outgoing.

items.name: hasConnected
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the call has connected.

items.name: hasEnded
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the call has ended.

items.name: isOnHold
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the call is on hold.
